# Serena MCP: ignore the cache CONTENTS, memories, local override, and the global
# config serena writes into the repo root — but TRACK project.yml (its versioned
# config) and the cache symlink, so the frozen sandbox base (git archive of
# tracked files) inherits the Python LS config and the warm cache pointer.
.serena/*
!.serena/project.yml
!.serena/cache

